item.title: Need help im new to hamachi
item.dc:creator: @Fernando_Pena Fernando Pena
item.description:
@Fernando_Pena wrote:

just go to the “RS2 Server Advertisement” in the main menu and find a server you want to play open it if it says something like this

“Hamachi: Yes, hellz of pkz- hellz of pkz3 pass: 123”

you go to the triangle on the bottom of hamachi and click join net work and put in the “hellz of pkz” for the name and at the bottom you put the pass “123”

and then find the owner and right click the owners name and press “copy address” and then go to your moparscape on the top right click “file” then press “new server” and then paste in the address you copied of hamachi and there you go.
